[Name] ReBMP
[Summary] Revitalised BMP
[Description] A fork of the dead project Beep-Media-Player, which is a music player under Linux. Now it has new features: support ape lossless music file with cue sheet file; support FLAC lossless music files with cue sheet file; with a lyrics panel, show lyrics when playing.
[License] GPL V2
[Homepage] http://code.google.com/p/rebmp/
